<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.7">
<l>veḷḷai viḷicaṅkuveñ cuṭart tiruccakkara mēntukaiyaṉ</l>
<l>uḷḷaviṭam viṉavilu makkiṟaivam miṉcuvaṭu raikkēṉ</l>
<l>veḷḷaippura vikkurakku velkoṭit tērmicai muṉpuniṉṟu</l>
<l>kaḷḷappaṭaittu ṇaiyākip pāratamkai ceyyakkaṇ ṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you ask for the place where appears him with hands</l>
<l rend="indent">that bear the sounding white conch</l>
<l rend="indent">and the fiery, bright, divine discus,</l>
<l>come, I with give you a tiny hint.</l>
<l>There are those who saw [him] standing</l>
<l rend="indent">at the front of [his] chariot with a white horse</l>
<l rend="indent">and a monkey victory banner</l>
<l>when, as a sly friend to the army,</l>
<l>[he] lent [his] hand to the Bhārata war.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
